sequenceDiagram
    participant Administrator
    participant COUSR01C
    participant USRSEC File

    activate Administrator
    Administrator->>+COUSR01C: Submit New User Data
    activate COUSR01C
    COUSR01C->>+USRSEC File: Check for Duplicate User ID
    USRSEC File->>COUSR01C: User ID Availability
    alt User ID Exists
        COUSR01C->>Administrator: Display "User ID already exists" error
    else User ID is Unique
        COUSR01C->>+USRSEC File: Write New User Record
        USRSEC File-->>-COUSR01C: Write Confirmation
        COUSR01C->>Administrator: Display "User added successfully" message
    end
    deactivate Administrator
    deactivate COUSR01C